                               Command : SHARK

NAME
   shark - Purchase defaulted loan

Level: Expert

SYNTAX
   [##:##] Command : shark <LOAN #>

The  shark command is used to buy out an overdue loan from another owner.  The
<LOAN #> is the number of the loan you wish to buy.

     The loan must be in arrears.  The holder of the  note  will  recieve  the
value  of the loan plus one periods worth of interest from your treasury.  The
player who owes the money on the loan will be notified of the  switch.   After
the loan is transferred you may collect on it as normal.

SEE ALSO
   offer, consider, collect, financial, Loans

